{"tid":1101840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【丁地好好用】政府預留丁屋地ㅤ大到夠起公共屋邨","createTime":"2019-04-11T09:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T10:35:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"15db963c0679de2db926a8ce3f36b3ddb1c9a27e","tid":1101840,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"本土研究社2019/4/11 &mdash; 14:43<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g62Bk7u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg62Bk7u.png&h=977e6e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n丁權司法覆核裁定，政府以「私人協約」或「換地」方式批出官地予原居民建丁屋不屬基本法保障的「傳統權益」，意味著為此預留的 932 公頃「閒置政府丁地」應可釋放出來益全港市民。然而政務司司長張建宗率先開腔，指那 932 公頃大都零散、建屋潛力小，好多是走廊、空地、斜坡、行人路等（註 1）。<br />\n<br />\n司長看來好唔熟書〜 932 公頃的數字是來自發展局，已經扣除道路/通道、人造斜坡、臨時撥給政府的工地（註 2）。我們去年好認真地透過地圖工具，將 932 公頃閒置政府丁地逐塊檢視過，發現當中 32 公頃一點都不零碎（每塊逾 5,000 平方呎以上），而且鄰近道路、地形平坦、未有任何發展計劃，好有潛力釋放作公營房屋或社福設施發展。其中以下八塊靚地，均位處或鄰近新市鎮，絕不是山旮旯。從衛星圖中對比每幅地和旁邊樓盤的面積，就可見到塊地有幾好用！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEtT7NJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEtT7NJ.png&h=d6f91590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ue29F70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUe29F70.png&h=6f5b24f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/11/175536_59e5030204e59c7deb1f353a5066b392.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F11%2F175536_59e5030204e59c7deb1f353a5066b392.png&h=322d5ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/11/175555_00d9b0349ddc9afef1d1199052c9db23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F11%2F175555_00d9b0349ddc9afef1d1199052c9db23.png&h=de8c3e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/11/175615_9cfd97f4e7fc3b6edde04a2c6b4b10de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F11%2F175615_9cfd97f4e7fc3b6edde04a2c6b4b10de.png&h=7944aae0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/11/175636_967f83413483c9c0438ab730b7af3055.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F11%2F175636_967f83413483c9c0438ab730b7af3055.png&h=62c7ba10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/11/175657_92a0f37c89dcf03ac97ed02b83034e77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F11%2F175657_92a0f37c89dcf03ac97ed02b83034e77.png&h=384544da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/11/175716_c99f561d4d8eabfd6c9e9485f8574d4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F11%2F175716_c99f561d4d8eabfd6c9e9485f8574d4e.png&h=9cb32a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考《香港規劃標準與準則》，我們保守地按地積比 2.1 倍去推算，估計 32 公頃面積大、位置佳的閒置政府丁地若釋放出來，便可建約 11,000-14,000 間鄉郊式公屋。另外，932 公頃內其他面積較細小的地塊，亦可考慮用作過渡性房屋、社區設施等。而這些土地大都正在養草，地政處更要定期派人去剪草！與其浪費人力物力，不如立即釋放發展益市民啦〜<br />\n<br />\n註 1：《明報》〈本研社：6 鄉地夠大建屋邨〉（8-4-2019）<br />\n註 2：發展局 「未批租或撥用的政府土地的面積分析，以及標示有關地塊範圍的地圖」<br />\n<br />\n#大大塊地好好用 #釋放土地俾真正有需要人士用 #寧願養草都唔俾人用 #政府講夠大話未 #收埋靚地咪呃你支持東大嶼囉<br />\n<br />\n📗 隱藏丁地逐個捉：<br />\n《隱藏選項》報告<br />\n《隱藏選項》地圖<br />\n<br />\n支持丁屋研究計劃，拆穿官商鄉黑謊話！<br />\n<br />\n🔍 了解更多<br />\n💪🏽 支持我們<br />\n<br />\n本土研究社 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B8%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%BD%E7%94%A8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A0%90%E7%95%99%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%8B%E5%9C%B0%E1%85%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%A0%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E1%2585%25A0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%2582%25A8%2F&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=535de1d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E1%2585%25A0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%2582%25A8%2F&h=90f350ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B8%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%BD%E7%94%A8-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A0%90%E7%95%99%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%8B%E5%9C%B0%E1%85%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%A0%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8/</a>"},{"pid":"34bcba299f9f15346c9f0c1b8b16017a8c0cd635","tid":1101840,"uid":43438,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦<br />\n起公屋都唔係俾香港人住嘅"},{"pid":"614e3fd4e859be470c6aedcfede62a62ce1fcf8a","tid":1101840,"uid":886,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"起幾多公屋咪又係新移民住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試下公布下每條新公屋有幾多%人係來港未住夠7年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bda1ded1082f005de67f5465b1401bc16ff812","tid":1101840,"uid":70357,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"614e3fd4e859be470c6aedcfede62a62ce1fcf8a","tid":1101840,"uid":886,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"起幾多公屋咪又係新移民住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試下公布下每條新公屋有幾多%人係來港未住夠7年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"起私樓香港人買唔到比大陸人買<br />\n居屋係咪唯一反唔到<img src=